
---

## ▶️ How to Run the Project
1. Clone or download the repository.
2. Open in your favorite Java IDE.
3. Compile and run the `InventoryManagementSystem.java` file.
4. Use the menu options to perform inventory operations.

---

## 📸 Sample Output
=== Inventory Management System ===

Add Product

View Products

Update Quantity

Remove Product

Exit

